{"tid":2231694,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國漁船入境群撈 韓國海警要動武","createTime":"2020-10-06T00:13:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-06T06:40:35.000Z","uid":141151,"like":46,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"15ada783d18ddf8b8aacd36d3e6b9c7218aedc21","tid":2231694,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T00:13:35.000Z","msg":"中國漁船入境群撈 韓國海警要動武<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20201005-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%BC%81%E8%88%B9%E5%85%A5%E5%A2%83%E7%BE%A4%E6%92%88-%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E6%B5%B7%E8%AD%A6%E8%A6%81%E5%8B%95%E6%AD%A6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfi.fr%2Ftw%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F20201005-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25BC%2581%25E8%2588%25B9%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%25A2%2583%25E7%25BE%25A4%25E6%2592%2588-%25E9%259F%2593%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%25A6%2581%25E5%258B%2595%25E6%25AD%25A6&d=SBcu0iNh8WN0EYdC3CIZLw1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=9ac3dbb3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20201005-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%BC%81%E8%88%B9%E5%85%A5%E5%A2%83%E7%BE%A4%E6%92%88-%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E6%B5%B7%E8%AD%A6%E8%A6%81%E5%8B%95%E6%AD%A6</a><br />\n<br />\n近期在韓國西部海域進行非法捕撈的中國漁船激增，迫使韓國當局決定加強整治，不排除出動多人操作武器。<br />\n<br />\n據中央社今天報道稱，中國漁船違法捕撈猖獗，韓國海警擬動武因應。消息引述韓聯社，韓國中部地方海洋警察廳今天表示，在韓國西部海域的專屬經濟區（EEZ）附近出沒的非法中國漁船數量，10月以來日平均達360艘，較9月的199艘激增8成。<br />\n<br />\n韓國海警推測，韓國西部海域專屬經濟區今年漁獲量增加，加上2019冠狀病毒疾病影響，使當局只能以驅逐等消極方式因應，避免不必要接觸，進行非法捕撈的中國漁船因此更加猖獗。<br />\n<br />\n海警原在西部海域專屬經濟區部署2艘警備艦艇，9月22日起增至3艘，每次出航時間也從原本的8天7夜增至9天8夜。<br />\n<br />\n據該報道，此外，海警也將與海洋水產部轄下西海漁業管理團、海軍等單位合作，取締進犯韓方海域的非法中國漁船，不排除使用共用武器。共用武器是較一般步兵裝備更大型，以中隊級以下小規模隊伍為單位操作的多人操作武器。"},{"pid":"256b8d5e0233d7a570cca443323a75712e4f170a","tid":2231694,"uid":3465,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T00:25:43.000Z","msg":"支持韓國警察嚴正執法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8d7492706cf490bdaea6ac18f9986f2b75e68f6","tid":2231694,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T00:26:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0b04a09eaba10867de484bc64c4f72ea6777ad2","tid":2231694,"uid":39871,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T00:28:04.000Z","msg":"用子彈就可以避免不必要接觸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0464631ef72bc8f4fd3ffac400f228fd376d4b13","tid":2231694,"uid":7323,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T00:32:08.000Z","msg":"應該直接炸沉"},{"pid":"ab381b9f7a566e9fe00adb64108a8cb104f4462f","tid":2231694,"uid":188176,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"d0b04a09eaba10867de484bc64c4f72ea6777ad2","tid":2231694,"uid":39871,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T00:28:04.000Z","msg":"用子彈就可以避免不必要接觸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T00:32:37.000Z","msg":"one bullet one cure<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"483bd91102dd33a626107d889b631ed57ac71c16","tid":2231694,"uid":77196,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T00:33:19.000Z","msg":"直接槍殺班生蕃啦"},{"pid":"55712e9b71144f0983967002c17845c0e153a11b","tid":2231694,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T00:33:39.000Z","msg":"算鬼數啦，奶共文在寅同拜登一樣得把口 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c8e4a90de484ab370305b5a3b124035e74ca525","tid":2231694,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T00:42:25.000Z","msg":"支持韓國警察實彈執法"},{"pid":"abc1b76d79804d4d12ca7be82d46864d8d9369cf","tid":2231694,"uid":151074,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T00:45:08.000Z","msg":"導彈係最低武力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"h